data.description: Not a short sale or foreclosure - Quick Closing! Home shows PRIDE of ownership located in a cul-de-sac next to a beautiful common area maintained by HOA that leads to walking trails. Hardwood floors throughout ENTIRE home. Kitchen has upgraded sink and all black appliances with breakfast area and views family room. 2nd bedrooms are HUGE and appears to have 2 Masters. Large landing area, 4th bedroom could be office/nursery as it connects to Master. Large, fenced private wooded backyard with pavilion structure covering patio. A MUST SEE!
